            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>tamarind paste </strong>with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>garam masala </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1724830791725-x200.jpg",
